Author: cryptocryptics
Title: [ANN][ICO]Cryptics Exchange rate predictions based on AI
Body: CRYPTICS model will generate forecasts for different time periods based on several numerous sources. The outcome will be a predicted probability of the move direction and the expected value of its size, together with the accuracy estimates. The comprehensiveness of the input data and the predictions is one of the main advantages of using CRYPTICS, in contrast to a simple analysis of one or more data sources, or existing information panels. On a cold start we can already guarantee the prediction accuracy of 64% one day ahead, which we are aiming to improve up until 75% for the hot start.

Author: cryptocryptics
Title: [ANN][ICO]Cryptics Exchange rate predictions based on AI
Body: Hello! Thanks for the expressed opinion. 100% probability of predictions can not be achieved unless you have in your hands a volume for trading, capable of ruining the market (as it was recently). And then this is no longer a prediction. As for accuracy. Our AI analyzes information from more than 100,000 social resources (including exchanges, social networks, some media), the database will expand over time. This is a very large flow of information that allows you to create a forecast for different terms. Of course, if we take a sample of individual forecasts, we can say that the accuracy is reduced. But if you take the whole mass of forecasts for all time, it will be seen that the accuracy remains approximately in the same range. Thank you for your attention, we will work to improve the accuracy.

Author: dredyxt
Title: [ANN][ICO]Cryptics Exchange rate predictions based on AI
Body: Quote from: goodbounty on August 15, 2017, 07:08:47 PM  All answers and moderation are done via official Cryptics account: cryptocryptics  WEB Twitter Facebook Telegram Medium Whitepaper  https://i.imgur.com/RTEdjrQ.jpg  Cryptics – world`s first self-learning platform, that analyzes the cryptocurrency market and creates forecasts. Data collection and processing occurs in real time from variety of sources in order to capture and record all relevant signals. Cryptocurrency market is quite complicated and not understandable for offline investors. It takes high level of knowledge and many years of experience in order to understand current trends. High-qualified specialists in this field are just starting to appear and their knowledge is scattered and not systemized, so it is hard to form global reliable predictions.  All information mentioned above causes difficulties for medium and small private investors in dealing with cryptocurrencies.   Our Mission  Our mission is to give any person, whether it`s an investor, an export or a novice market participant an ability to find key information, based on which it will be easier to take most relevant decision regarding the mining, buying or selling the cryptocurrency, creation of portfolios of cryptocurrencies. Cryptics will stimulate scientific research in the field of artificial intelligence, as well as contribute to the further development of the blockchain, offering an infrastructure for creating funds for small and successful trades.   http://s018.radikal.ru/i517/1708/53/aa158b18a532.jpg http://s002.radikal.ru/i198/1708/15/24650915c4d0.jpg  http://s019.radikal.ru/i624/1708/67/a4308a6d2ea5.jpg  Cryptics Token Release   Fundraising and release of Cryptics tokens is intended to finance the development of the platform, the functionality of the self-learning part of the platform based on AI, as well as the development of a decentralized system for the collection and data updates. In addition, some part of the funds will be used for marketing and advertising needs. Cryptics tokens will be used to pay for any services that the platform provides. A total of 100.000.000 CRYPTICS tokens (CRP) will be provided: •66 million CRP will be sold from presale till ITO •31 million CRP will be reserved for the team, partners and advisors •3 million Bounty campaign  https://i.imgur.com/Pq2EnHA.png    The ITO will start on 08 March 2018. A total of 66.000.000 CRP CRYPTICS tokens will be provided. The cost of 1 CRP is estimated to be 0,001 ETH.  Collected funds will be used to develop a self-learning platform based on artificial intelligence, global marketing of the project, the creation of a sales department and contextual advertising. Cryptics will start accepting CRP tokens as payment for services in the platform.  https://i.imgur.com/52T2WKN.jpg   WEB Twitter Facebook Telegram Medium Whitepaper

Author: cryptocryptics
Title: [ANN][ICO]Cryptics Exchange rate predictions based on AI
Body: Arbitrating between different exchanges is a game of speed, not that of an intellect. We are instead giving our clients intelligent forecasts which are focused on within-exchange movements. That's much harder of a job, but much wider opportunities.

Author: cryptocryptics
Title: [ANN][ICO]Cryptics Exchange rate predictions based on AI
Body: Yes we do, we do have experts on HFT working in our team, who developed related algorithms for several years on conventional exchanges. They also suggested to tell you that often sending hundreds of orders per second while technically doable, would be banned on most of exchanges as a suspicious activity (see non-compliant behavior). HFT is more about the reaction speed, rather than spamming the matching engines.

Author: cryptocryptics
Title: [ANN][ICO]Cryptics Exchange rate predictions based on AI
Body: The CRYPTICS MVP demonstrates a fully functional dashboard for users and already highlights the main advantages of the system and its main competitive factors:  * High frequency trading forecast, day-to-day forecasts with high accuracy and a profit & loss calculator.  * Social media analysis for the forecast engine, allowing the program to analyse data flows from the internet, pinpointing key terms and evaluating them on a complex scoring model using machine learning and AI.  * The analytical part is a key element of the CRYPTICS system as experience indicates that cryptocurrency prices are largely formed by hype, social behaviour and speculative factors that propagate in a viral manner throughout the internet.  * Technical analysis is also integrated into CRYPTICS algorithms as AI forecasts indicators such as RSI, MACD, Bollinger bands, Ichimoku, SMA, EMA and etc.

Author: cryptocryptics
Title: [ANN][ICO]Cryptics Exchange rate predictions based on AI
Body: As a first step we finalize the CRYPTICS algorithm that is focused on predicting changes in prices of cryptocurrencies (including the ICO tokens) both with respect to the fiat currencies and to each other. Due to the fact that cryptocurrency markets are very new, the factors that drive prices are coming from very different sources, so the algorithm uses the method of Artificial Intelligence (AI) such as Machine Learning (ML), and specifically Deep Learning (DL), in order to combine quantitative (e.g. prices) and non-quantitative (e.g. news) data to come with a stable and reliable prediction. The collection of data and its processing occurs is done real-time, and leads to predictions time horizons ranging from minutes to days. These predictions can be used by any customer of the CRYPTICS platform either for private purposes (personal investments), or to build a trading strategy and create a small fund on this platform.   U can get the detailed information here:  https://cryptics.tech/Whitepaper-Cryptics-EN.pdf

Body: Dear Cryptics community!  We have decided to launch a New Bounty campaign.  Rules: this campaign includes following programs:  ⁃ youtube bounty  ⁃ reddit bounty  ⁃ telegram bounty  ⁃ vk.com bounty  ⁃ art works and other creative ideas bounty.  For this campaign 1% of the total number of Cryptics tokens will be allocated. Participants in all the programs of Bounty Facebook, Bounty Twitter, signature bounty, bounty transfers, bounty for blogs, bounty for inviting new members, continue to participate on the same terms, and a new campaign for this rewards will not be affected.  NEW Bounty campaign (start 26,10,2017)  Bounty vk.com  10% of bounty pool Is allocated for this campaign.  Conditions:  300+ subscribers  Public profile  Subscribe to our official Crryptics VK group https://vk.com/public155019401  Like and repost Cryptics activity  minimum 3 times a week  Write posts about Cryptics using all of the following hashtags 1 time per week minimum: #AI #Cryptics #ICO #Crowdsale #Bitcoin #Blockchain #Token #ETH #Ethereum #TokenSale  Do reposts on a regular basis, not missing a week.  Bounty participants’ list will be updated once a week. To get a bounty token reward listed participants must participate until the end of token sale. Multiple account registration is prohibited. Fake accounts usage is prohibited. All the activity from such accounts won’t be counted and paid in tokens.  Registration link: https://goo.gl/forms/vfDSJTOHYcB5EqH52  Bounty youtube  20% of the New Bounty campaign will be allocated for this campaign.  To participate in the youtube bounty, you need to create a video about the Cryptics project, and publish it on your channel.  Rules: - At least 500 subscribers on the channel. - Channel topic - ICO, crypto-currencies, trading, earnings on the Internet. - The video should last 2 minutes minimum - Negative videos do not participate in the campaign - There should be links to the official website of Cryptics,  the social network, and the Bitcointalk thread in the video description.  Main evaluation criteria is the quality of the published material, traffic and significance for Cryptics and the blocking community as a whole.  Registration link: https://goo.gl/forms/AO1AcfFAMsrxUHTh1  Bounty reddit  15% of the New Bounty campaign will be allocated to this campaign.  Requirements: - You must publish an article in reddit about the Cryptics project - Your account must exist for at least 20 days and have at least 10 posts or comments - The article should be published in subreddit with more than 100 readers - You can get + 50% to the reward for publishing posts in subreddit: r / bitcoin, r / ethereum, r / ethtrader, r / icocrypto, r / cryptocurrency, r / blockchain - No negative posts. - Any kind of spam is prohibited. - External posts should contain link to the official Cryptics website or to the bitcointalk thread (English or Russian). Main evaluation criteria is the quality of the published material, traffic and significance for Cryptics and the blocking community as a whole.  Registration link: https://goo.gl/forms/HrDMP1lEljxbruro2    Bounty subscribers telegram  15% of the New Bounty campaign will be allocated for this campaign. To participate, you must subscribe to the official Cryptics group in telegram. Publish at least 5 messages per week in the Cryptics channel. In your posts, you can ask questions, or leave comments related to the Cryptics project.   Registration link: https://goo.gl/forms/EgvDtrB4DB4ARbwS2  Bounty of telegram publications  15% of the New Bounty campaign will be allocated for this campaign If you own your own group or channel in telegrams, you can publish posts, news or video about the Cryptics project and get paid for it.  Rules: The materials must include links to the official Cryptics website, official social networking pages, or links to the Bitcointalk forum threads. Main evaluation criteria is the quality of the published material, traffic and significance for Cryptics and the blocking community as a whole.  Registration link: https://goo.gl/forms/4rMPIeJg0pNJ2Xe72    Artwork Campaign   15% of the New Bounty campaign will be allocated for this campaign Rules: Create a positive meme / sticker + Crypto currency / brand logo Cryptics + share in FB, Twitter, vk or Telegram Your work should contain a reference to Cryptics, or a link to the official website, social network or bitcointalk thread(s). Resulting artworks may do not have the links but include following hashtags: #AI #Cryptics # ICO #Crowdsale #Bitcoin #Blockchain #Token #ETH #Ethereum #TokenSaleArt Work must be original;  In order for your work to be credited, you must send it (or a link) to one of the official threads of Cryptics for bitcointalk. Main evaluation criteria is the quality of the published material, traffic and significance for Cryptics and the community community as a whole.  Registration link: https://goo.gl/forms/qKRVOCxo55vQctfm1

Author: goodbounty
Title: [ANN][ICO]Cryptics Exchange rate predictions based on AI
Body: All answers and moderation are done via official Cryptics account: cryptocryptics  WEB Twitter Facebook Telegram Medium Whitepaper    Cryptics – world`s first self-learning platform, that analyzes the cryptocurrency market and creates forecasts. Data collection and processing occurs in real time from variety of sources in order to capture and record all relevant signals. Cryptocurrency market is quite complicated and not understandable for offline investors. It takes high level of knowledge and many years of experience in order to understand current trends. High-qualified specialists in this field are just starting to appear and their knowledge is scattered and not systemized, so it is hard to form global reliable predictions.  All information mentioned above causes difficulties for medium and small private investors in dealing with cryptocurrencies.   Our Mission  Our mission is to give any person, whether it`s an investor, an export or a novice market participant an ability to find key information, based on which it will be easier to take most relevant decision regarding the mining, buying or selling the cryptocurrency, creation of portfolios of cryptocurrencies. Cryptics will stimulate scientific research in the field of artificial intelligence, as well as contribute to the further development of the blockchain, offering an infrastructure for creating funds for small and successful trades.        Cryptics Token Release   Fundraising and release of Cryptics tokens is intended to finance the development of the platform, the functionality of the self-learning part of the platform based on AI, as well as the development of a decentralized system for the collection and data updates. In addition, some part of the funds will be used for marketing and advertising needs. Cryptics tokens will be used to pay for any services that the platform provides. A total of 100.000.000 CRYPTICS tokens (CRP) will be provided: •66 million CRP will be sold from presale till ITO •31 million CRP will be reserved for the team, partners and advisors •3 million Bounty campaign      The ITO will start on 08 March 2018. A total of 66.000.000 CRP CRYPTICS tokens will be provided. The cost of 1 CRP is estimated to be 0,001 ETH.  Collected funds will be used to develop a self-learning platform based on artificial intelligence, global marketing of the project, the creation of a sales department and contextual advertising. Cryptics will start accepting CRP tokens as payment for services in the platform.     WEB Twitter Facebook Telegram Medium Whitepaper
